var tokens = tokenizer.Tokenize(text);
```

5. Convert the tokens to input features that can be fed into the BERT model.

```csharp
using BertModel;
...
var features = InputFeatures.FromTokens(tokens, maxSeqLength: 128);
```

6. Create a TensorFlow session and feed the input features to the BERT model to obtain the embeddings.

```csharp
using System.Linq;
...
using var session = new TFSession(model.Graph);
